  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To compare the safety and tolerability of brimonidine tartrate ophthalmic solution 0.025%
      versus its vehicle in a population of pediatric, adult, and geriatric subjects. At least 51%
      of subjects will be 40 years of age or older.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
