  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Participants must be at least 5 years of age at Visit 1 of either sex gender and any
             race or ethnicity;

          -  Have ocular health within normal limits, including a calculated best- corrected (if
             necessary) visual acuity of 0.3 logMAR or better in each eye, as measured using an
             Early Treatment of Diabetic Retinopathy Study (ETDRS) chart.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Have any ocular/systemic health problems

          -  Use of any disallowed medications during the period indicated prior to Visit 1 and for
             the duration of the study.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
